1
00:00:00,370 --> 00:00:03,029
What the hell is this?

2
00:00:03,029 --> 00:00:06,440
This is Michael Morris's will.

3
00:00:06,440 --> 00:00:09,890
His lawyer sent it to us right after his death.

4
00:00:09,890 --> 00:00:13,250
After my death, I wished to hand over my business

5
00:00:13,250 --> 00:00:15,890
to my granddaughter, Jade Morris.

6
00:00:15,890 --> 00:00:20,890
On one condition, she must never, under any circumstances,

7
00:00:20,890 --> 00:00:23,089
threaten or harm Marco Sanchez.

8
00:00:23,089 --> 00:00:25,769
Never, under any circumstances,

9
00:00:25,769 --> 00:00:28,050
are you sure you want that in writing?

10
00:00:28,050 --> 00:00:31,289
What if Marco makes the first move against you?

11
00:00:31,289 --> 00:00:35,009
Marco may be reckless, but his heart is good.

12
00:00:35,009 --> 00:00:37,689
He just needs more time to grow.

13
00:00:37,689 --> 00:00:39,530
I don't believe this.

14
00:00:39,530 --> 00:00:41,210
This is true.

15
00:00:41,210 --> 00:00:43,210
You're lying.

